race.comment: INSTANT ACTION (8) is a promising dog in the frame at three of nine starts including three wins and was a last start winner (24.02) over 425m at Bendigo. Performs well off this draw. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. REV TREASURE (2) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 390m behind Uncle Ernest (22.96) in a Grade 5. One of the main contenders. NALA'S GHOST (1) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the money last time though when second (22.38) at this track. Form here sound including three wins. Expected to feature. PRETTY PANAMA (3) cannot be ruled out.
